then consider k being Nat such that A13: x in ( N . k ) and A14: (for r being Nat holds (x in ( N . r ) implies k <= r));
A15: ((ex l being Nat st k = ( l + 1 )) implies (ex s being (Element of ( NAT )) st x in ( F . s )))
